Package com.ansi.scilla.report.reportBuilder.reportBy

Interface ReportByDivision

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DispatchedOutstandingTicketReport, InvoiceRegisterReport, PacActivationListReport, PacCancelledListReport, PacDetailReport, PacProposedListReport, PacReport, PacSummaryReport, PastDueReport, PastDueReport2, SixMonthRollingVolumeReport, SixMonthRollingVolumeSummary, SixMonthRollingVolumeSummary, SmrvDetailReport, SmrvReport, TicketStatusReport
    public interface ReportByDivision
    When a report implements this interface, it is indicating that it is generated on a division by division basis. It is not an indication that the division is the only parameter. (eg. ReportByDivEnd can also be implemented)
    Author:
    dclewis
